data.title: Contact Us
data.meta_description: The official website of the New Jersey Motor Vehicle Commission.
data.text:
Phone numbers by topic can be found here.

Our customer service lines may experience high call volumes. As an alternative, you can email us your question or concern. Customer service representatives are available from 8:30 a.m. to 4:15 p.m., Monday through Friday. Our chatbot general information and pre-recorded information is available at all other times.

If you are deaf or hard of hearing, please use 7-1-1 NJ Relay.
